<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#47689c8c47e80b7ef5b3bf653efbf18c>.
<#47689c8c47e80b7ef5b3bf653efbf18c> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/9409cb12-20c0-4b39-9131-aded01b7ba85>;
