_:b0__15784 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((9.32 69.42,29.80 69.42,29.80 53.87,9.32 53.87,9.32 69.42))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
