<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#773a1f74576bfaf58ee8c183d4c1344c>.
<#773a1f74576bfaf58ee8c183d4c1344c> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://catalog.lansstyrelsen.se/store/2/resource/89>;
