<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#a18adfea3704206ccf5fdcaa53bb5a93>.
<#a18adfea3704206ccf5fdcaa53bb5a93> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/e7c05e67-a237-43bd-aa32-84b539a6852f>;
