<#c82f318378740f16b82b2cee4c794c52> {
<https://www.geodata.se/resources/b8bbb27b-4aa5-4244-aeea-6c76f868d109> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/CONT>;
